data.description: Escape to the serene outskirts of Zimmerman and country living on this expansive 3-acre property. This well-maintained home features three bedrooms and two bathrooms on the upper level. The kitchen is a culinary delight with granite countertops, glass subway tile backsplash, and stainless-steel appliances, complemented by a spacious walk-in pantry. Entertain in this home with a lower-level wet bar room and a recreational area. Privacy is paramount at the end of a cul-de-sac street, with a sizable backyard with no visible neighbors. Enjoy outdoor living with a 16' x 21' deck and a substantial 14' x 21' concrete patio. This property is more than a home; it's a retreat. The roof, upgraded 1 1/2 years ago, boasts architectural shingles. The crown jewel is the fully finished, heated 36' x 50' shop. This 1,800 sq ft steel haven features 14 ft sidewalls, (2) 12 ft overhead doors, water supply, floor drains, and an expansive concrete apron and side slab. Don't miss the chance to call it yours.
